    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents a base decorator for attack items, allowing additional behavior to be layered on top of an existing <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1attack_1_1_attack_item" kindref="compound">AttackItem</ref> instance. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class implements the Decorator Design Pattern. It wraps another <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1attack_1_1_attack_item" kindref="compound">AttackItem</ref> and forwards all property calls to the wrapped item unless overridden by subclasses. Concrete decorators can modify <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1attack_1_1_attack_decorator_1a7575a7cda9e9284912427a35b68881da" kindref="member">Hit</ref>, <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1attack_1_1_attack_decorator_1a4f4491c445a596cd899cf3986b8bd38b" kindref="member">Range</ref>, <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1attack_1_1_attack_decorator_1a15ef1af98f28a62da8aa51d19fde625e" kindref="member">Weight</ref>, or other behavior without changing the underlying item. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
